Class BSTree<E extends Comparable<? super E>>

java.lang.Object
implementations.BSTree<E>
Type Parameters:
E - Generic datatype must be comparable and Serializable
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, BSTreeADT<E>
public class BSTree<E extends Comparable<? super E>> extends Object implements BSTreeADT<E>, Serializable
This class is the implementation of the Binary Search Tree based on the provided BSTreeADT
